headline: Klearcom establishes US office with 20 new jobs
summary: NEWARK, N.J., September 23, 2025--Klearcom launches US office with 20 new jobs, enhancing global telecom testing, CX monitoring and contact center assurance.

headline: Alipay+ and Mastercard Bring Overseas NFC Payments to Kakao Pay Users
summary: SINGAPORE, September 23, 2025--Alipay+, a global wallet gateway under Ant International, supports Kakao Pay, a leading South Korean mobile wallet, in launching NFC (Near-Field Communication) payment for overseas transactions, through its partnership with Mastercard. Kakao Pay becomes one of the first Alipay+ mobile payment partners to introduce the convenient and secure "tap-to-pay" experiences when its users travel abroad.
